messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacation Village Resorts. This is Jamie, a virtual agent on a recorded line. How can I help you today?
Paying my annual fee.
Who do I have the pleasure of speaking with?
Devin Hobbs.
Alright Devin, can you share the phone number you have on your contract?
Five four one
eight zero six four eight five one.
Just a sec, let me check that for you.
I was able to pull up a record using your phone number. Can you confirm your state of residence?
Oregon.
Great, your information is verified. Go ahead and let me know what you need help with regarding your annual fee.
Make a payment.

You have a maintenance balance of one thousand four dollars and sixty five cents for The Grandview at Las Vegas, contract number four zero six two four zero. Would you like to make a payment for this property?
Yes.
The email I have on file is htsshell@gmail.com and the phone number is five four one three eight seven four four four four. Are these correct?
Yes.
Hang tight, I’m sending your payment link now.
Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No.
Oh, yes.
Yes.
Alright, what else do you need help with?
I need to change the phone number.
Your request is best handled by our concierge department, please hold while I get you connected

Thank you for calling the concierge department for the Vacation Village family of resorts, where owner satisfaction is our top priority. We apologize for the brief wait, and we appreciate your patience. Our hours of operatio n are 8:30 AM to 6:00 PM Eastern Standard Time. We understand that sometimes nothing beats speaking to a real person. Our team is working diligently to ensure your call is answered as soon as possible. In the meantime, why no t explore our website and discover all that Vacation Village Resorts has to offer? Our website is a valuable resource filled with product information, frequently asked questions, important contact information for mortgage service s and maintenance fee payments, and much more. Save time and find the answers you need at vacationvillageresorts.com. For real-time assistance, we encourage you to try out our Text Us Now feature. Simply visit our website and loo k for the Text Us button at the bottom right corner of the screen. With just a few taps, you can connect with one of our dedicated agents who will be happy to assist you promptly. At Vacation Village Resorts, we believe in providing exceptional customer service at every touchpoint. If you prefer to remain on the line, rest assured that your call is essential to us, and we'll be with you shortly.
